fp8_fast seems to cause huge quality degradation

fp_16_fast enables "Full FP16 Accmumulation in FP16 GEMMs" feature available in the very latest pytorch nightly, this is around 20% speed boost. 

Sageattn if you have it installed can be used for almost double inference speed

TeaCache could be considered to be sort of an automated step skipper 

The relative l1 threshold -value determines how aggressive this is, higher values are faster but quality suffers more. Very first steps should NEVER be skipped with this model or it kills the motion. When using the pre-calculated coefficients, the treshold value should be much higher than with the default coefficients.
Enhance-a-video can increase the fidelity of the results, too high values lead to noisy results.

You can use either the original clip vision or the normal comfyui clip vision loader, they are the same model in the end.

Adjust the blocks to swap based on your VRAM, this is a tradeoff between speed and memory usage.

Alternatively there's option to use VRAM management introduced in DiffSynt-Studios. This is usually slower, but saves even more VRAM compared to BlockSwap

The man's body tumbles through the air, his arms flailing wildly as he loses his grip on the surfboard, and his head disappears below the surface of the turquoise water, sending ripples through the calm surface. As he plunges downwards, the camera follows, a low-angle shot from beneath the water's surface, the sunlight filtering down in shimmering shafts. Suddenly, the scene erupts into a blaze of flames, a fiery explosion that engulfs the pool, and a man in a sleek black suit emerges from the inferno, his chiseled features illuminated by the intense heat, his piercing blue eyes fixed intently on the camera. The black suit is tailored to perfection, accentuating his broad shoulders and powerful physique. The tropical setting remains visible in the background, with palm trees swaying in the distance, their green canopies a stark contrast to the fiery chaos. The camera zooms in on the man's face, a mix of determination and intensity etched on his features, as the flames dance around him. The scene is captured in a studio..
the man in the pool falls below the frame into the water, and the scene erupts into an explosion out of which a man in a black suit emerges from the flames
